Russian man was filming a documentary in snow-covered mountains when he was struck by a falling icicle which caused a blood clot and swelling in his leg . 
  He was unable to walk and decided to perform surgery on himself using items in his first aid kit . 
  He used a gas lamp, a scalpel and surgical string to remove the clot . 
  He then sewed the wound up with surgical string and the wound healed . 
 